CatDescriptText: Portrait of a seated man in U.S. Army uniform.  He is a corporal in the U.S. Army Infantry, wearing Expert and Sharpshooter Arms Qualification Badges and a ribbon (possibly representing a Good Conduct Medal).
TitMainTitle: Portrait of man wearing U. S. Army uniform, light colored tie, moustache, two Maltese crosses on chest, Field Artillery insignia on lapel, and Corporal patch on sleeve, posed on rug covered bench in front of light colored background, in Harris Studio
